          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The tritium target consisted of tritium gas absorbed in",
                "a 0.94 mg/cm2 thick titanium layer, which had been",
                "evaporated onto a gold backing"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The relative differential cross section of the",
                "3H(p,gamma)4He reaction was determined by normalizing",
                "at each angle, the gamma-ray yield of the moveable",
                "NaI crystal to that recorded by the monitor crystal."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "NAICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two 12.7 cm diam x 15.2 cm long crystal",
                "rotating over the angular range from 0 to 135 degr.",
                "The monitor crystal was set at the fixed angle 90 degr.",
                "with the direction of the proton beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error in the gamma-ray yield depended on",
                "the angle: at backward angles it consisted mainly of",
                "the statistical error (3-6%) ; at forward angles it",
                "was the sum of ERR-1, ERR-2, ERR-S."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The error in the gamma-ray absorption in the",
                "target holder (7%)"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": 4.0,
                "maximum_value": 10.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " statistical error (4-10%)"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-2",
                "minimum_value": 2.0,
                "maximum_value": 8.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainty in the multiple",
                "scattering correction at the angle 0. degr., estimated",
                "to range from 2 to 8% depending on the proton energy."
              ]
            }
          ],
